data.description: Welcome home to 4806 Lincoln Ct. in Carson City.     Don’t miss your opportunity to own a home with your own private movie room! Complete with an Espson Cinnema Projector with 120” steel framed felt screen, Onkyo receiver and surround sound. This epic movie room is compatible with IPhones and Firestick. This single-family home sits on the corner lot of a cul-de-sac. This home is move-in ready! Nestled in a quiet North East Carson neighborhood, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has many recent upgrades; including interior & exterior paint, new flooring, new HVAC system, newer appliances, including a brand new dishwasher, and a new garbage disposal in the kitchen.   No HOA! Schedule your private showing today and start creating unforgettable memories in this beautiful Carson City home.
